### HYMN XXX

#### A charm to be used when the eyes are anointed

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0703001">1</span></span>Heaven,
Earth, and Mitra here have caused mine eyes to be-  
   anointed well,  
  Savitar, Brāhmanaspati take care that they be duly balmed!

